column2: PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(STRLEN(?o)) AS ?checksum) { ?s rdfs:label ?o . }

column1: result-size-tiny [Export 10 tuples]

column1: result-size-medium [Export 100K tuples]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT ?s ?o WHERE { ?s schema:description ?o } LIMIT 100000

column1: result-size-large [Export 1M tuples]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT ?s ?o WHERE { ?s schema:description ?o } LIMIT 1000000

column1: result-size-xlarge [Export 10M tuples]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT ?s ?o WHERE { ?s schema:description ?o } LIMIT 10000000

column1: numeric-baseline [Baseline for numeric queries]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(?o) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:version ?o }

column1: numeric-abs [ABS function]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(ABS(?o)) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:version ?o }

column1: numeric-ceil [CEIL function]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(CEIL(?o)) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:version ?o }

column1: numeric-floor [FLOOR function]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(FLOOR(?o)) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:version ?o }

column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(ROUND(?o)) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:version ?o }

column1: numeric-add [Addition]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(?o + ?o) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:version ?o }

column1: numeric-greater [Greater than]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(?o > 0) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:version ?o }

column1: numeric-filter-bin-search-fifty-fifty [Numeric FILTER that filters out 50 percent of the values]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) { ?s schema:version ?o . FILTER (?o >= 2147882675) }

column1: numeric-filter-bin-search-seventy-thirty [Numeric FILTER that filters out 70 percent of the values]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) { ?s schema:version ?o . FILTER (?o >= 2241500354) }

column1: numeric-filter-bin-search-ninetyfive-five [Numeric FILTER that filters out 95 percent of the values]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) { ?s schema:version ?o . FILTER (?o >= 2325672138) }

column1: filter-few-results [FILTER that filters out most rows and has few results]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) { ?s schema:description ?o . FILTER (?s = ?o) }

column1: filter-many-results [FILTER that filters out few rows and has many results]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) { ?s schema:description ?o . FILTER (?s != ?o) }

column1: filter-language-en [FILTER on string predicate for only English literals]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) { ?s schema:description ?o . FILTER(LANG(?o) = "en") }

column1: date-year [YEAR function]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(YEAR(?o)) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:dateModified ?o }

column1: date-month [MONTH function]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(MONTH(?o)) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:dateModified ?o }

column1: date-day [DAY function]
column2: PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/> SELECT (SUM(DAY(?o)) AS ?sum) WHERE { ?s schema:dateModified ?o }

column1: number-of-triples [Total number of triples]
column2: SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) WHERE { ?s ?p ?o }

column1: number-of-subjects [Total number of distinct subjects]
column2: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?s) AS ?count) WHERE { ?s ?p ?o }

column1: number-of-predicates [Total number of distinct predicates]
column2: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?p) AS ?count) WHERE { ?s ?p ?o }

column1: number-of-objects [Total number of distinct objects]
column2: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?o) AS ?count) WHERE { ?s ?p ?o }

column1: number-of-literals [Total number of literals]
column2: SELECT (COUNT(?o) AS ?count) WHERE { ?s ?p ?o FILTER ISLITERAL(?o) }

column1: number-of-blank-nodes [Total number of blank nodes]
column2: SELECT (COUNT(?s) AS ?count) WHERE { ?s ?p ?o FILTER ISBLANK(?s) }
